      • getPackageNames

        public static Set<String> getPackageNames(ClassLoader aClassLoader)
                                   throws CheckstyleException
        Returns the set of package names, compiled from all checkstyle_packages.xml files found on the given classloaders classpath.
        パラメータ:
        aClassLoader - the class loader for loading the checkstyle_packages.xml files.
        戻り値:
        the set of package names.
        例外:
        CheckstyleException - if an error occurs.
